Given these two files, what does `main.cpp` print?

```cpp
// util.h
int triple(int x);
```

```cpp
// util.cpp
int triple(int x) { return x * 3; }
```

```cpp
// main.cpp
#include "util.h"
#include <iostream>
int main() {
    std::cout << triple(4) << "\n";
    return 0;
}
```

